00:03:19.530 --> 00:03:21.890
It is a very rational process in

00:03:21.890 --> 00:03:23.610
which you have a lot of information

00:03:23.610 --> 00:03:26.510
and in which all brands are

00:03:26.510 --> 00:03:28.010
competing for you, offer you

00:03:28.010 --> 00:03:29.030
discounts, etc.

