The Ferrari is the Ferrari,

00:03:44.270 --> 00:03:47.370
the Lamborghini is the Lamborghini,

00:03:47.570 --> 00:03:49.230
and the Ferrari is

00:03:49.230 --> 00:03:50.670
the Lamborghini.

00:03:51.690 --> 00:03:54.490
All this makes the margin, as

00:03:54.490 --> 00:03:55.870
your differentiation is greater,

00:03:55.870 --> 00:03:57.010
your margin usually usually

00:03:57.010 --> 00:03:58.050
is greater.

00:03:58.630 --> 00:03:59.510
Because the customer is less

00:03:59.510 --> 00:04:01.430
price sensitive and because you

00:04:01.430 --> 00:04:02.450
wear less in the competitive

