struggle with the rest.

00:04:05.190 --> 00:04:08.150
Another factor that is consequence is that

00:04:08.150 --> 00:04:11.370
you usually have more loyal customers.

00:04:11.450 --> 00:04:12.390
As you get more differentiated,

00:04:12.390 --> 00:04:13.450
you usually have more

00:04:13.450 --> 00:04:14.230
loyal customers.

