Well, in principle, it is something

00:04:35.410 --> 00:04:37.150
you should already understand because

00:04:37.150 --> 00:04:39.230
we study it in external analysis, in

00:04:39.450 --> 00:04:40.710
principle it makes more sense, there

00:04:41.030 --> 00:04:42.270
is more space for differentiation

00:04:42.270 --> 00:04:43.430
in some sectors than in

00:04:43.430 --> 00:04:44.150
others.

00:04:45.050 --> 00:04:46.830
There are sectors that are more diverse.

